DEFINITIONS

"Software" means RogueOS and all source code, documentation, tooling, and
associated files in this repository.

"You" means the individual or legal entity exercising rights under this License.

"Individual Use" means use by a natural person for personal projects, learning,
research, or experimentation — not on behalf of a company or organisation.

"Non-Commercial Organisation" means a registered non-profit, educational
institution, or government body acting in a non-commercial capacity.

"Small Business" means a legal entity whose total gross annual revenue across
all products and services does not exceed USD $1,000,000 (one million US dollars)
in the most recently completed fiscal year.

"Commercial Use" means use in connection with a business, product, or service
that generates — or is intended to generate — revenue.

"Enterprise" means any legal entity whose total gross annual revenue exceeds
USD $1,000,000 in the most recently completed fiscal year, including any entity
that is a subsidiary, affiliate, or division of such a company.

"Embed" means including the Software, or a substantial portion of it, as a
component of a hardware device, appliance, firmware image, or SaaS platform
that you distribute or provide to third parties.

